data.description: Revel in unobstructed ocean views and partial northern and southern panoramas. The fully renovated kitchen with top of the line appliances are a culinary delight. This home is brimming with updates in every room, ensuring modern comfort and style. With year around views of whales and wildlife, daily beach walks, large deck and fenced yard its the perfect blend of beauty and practicality. Embrace safety and serenity in this coastal gem, situated outside tsunami & flood zone. You're coastal retreat awaits!
